<template>
    <v-layout>
      <v-navigation-drawer
        v-model="drawer"
        :rail="rail"
        permanent
        @click="rail = false"
      >
        <v-list>
          <v-list-item
            prepend-avatar="/avatar.png"
            title="WLPH"
          >
            <template v-slot:append>
              <v-btn
                icon="mdi-chevron-left"
                variant="text"
                @click.stop="rail = !rail"
              ></v-btn>
            </template>
          </v-list-item>
        </v-list>

        <v-divider></v-divider>

        <v-list density="compact" nav>
          <!-- HOME -->
          <v-list-item
            prepend-icon="mdi-home"
            title="Home"
            to="/"
            exact
            />
            <!-- BOOKINGS -->
            <v-list-item
            prepend-icon="mdi-flag-triangle"
            title="Bookings"
            to="/bookings"
            exact
            />
             <!-- QUOTATIONS -->
            <v-list-item
            prepend-icon="mdi-flag-triangle"
            title="quotations"
            to="/quotations"
            exact
            />
           <!-- ABOUT -->
            <v-list-item
            prepend-icon="mdi-information"
            title="About"
            to="/about"
            />
          
        </v-list>
      </v-navigation-drawer>
      <v-main style="min-height: 100vh;">
      <router-view />
    </v-main>
    </v-layout>
</template>


<script setup>

  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const drawer = ref(true)
  const rail = ref(true)


</script>
